#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:2 f419da67f23c46f2b6abff3e1a24510e
msgid "Example Gallery"
msgstr "示例画廊"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:4 07b7eb28ab3a46e89e8f01b39d369ab0
msgid ""
"Hands-on, runnable examples — from FEM building-block visualizations, "
"through canonical PDE solves, to research-grade fluid, solid, and "
"electromagnetic problems. Each page maps the underlying mathematics to a "
"concrete TensorMesh script you can run."
msgstr ""
"可动手运行的示例——从有限元方法基础构件的可视化，到经典偏微分方程的求解，再到研究级别的流体、固体与电磁问题。每个页面都将底层数学映射到一段可直接运行的具体"
" TensorMesh 脚本。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:12 be61ac1ab448456b9c94058f986778b7
msgid "Basics & Visualization"
msgstr "基础与可视化"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:17 a1b39cf457974510b94ccb96a0269ebe
msgid ""
"Basis points, shape functions, element ordering, and a mesh-generation "
"gallery."
msgstr "基函数节点、形函数、单元编号，以及网格生成画廊。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:19 1aa7a1f072274b8d95d4287a1313b1d3
msgid "Poisson Equation"
msgstr "泊松方程"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:24 f764d6d88c924a1080bb3cfb4cfaf83a
msgid ""
"Elliptic PDE in 2D / 3D, batched RHS, and h-adaptive refinement on the "
"L-shape."
msgstr "二维 / 三维椭圆型偏微分方程、批量右端项，以及在 L 形区域上的 h-自适应加密。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:26 c574e19ddffc41b991cb9c15af2b964e
msgid "Diffusion"
msgstr "扩散"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:31 fac5eb4d22214c9abd673c8356e09852
msgid ""
"Transient heat equation and nonlinear Allen-Cahn phase-field evolution."
msgstr "瞬态热方程与非线性 Allen-Cahn 相场演化。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:33 8ff9d58c318f4d36b22f34954caf618d
msgid "Wave Equation"
msgstr "波动方程"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:38 77b2b67fe1064f63a52fec2a1d44bbcb
msgid "Hyperbolic PDE with explicit central-difference time stepping."
msgstr "采用显式中心差分时间步进的双曲型偏微分方程。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:40 a2b46870143443a4b0e3a0b4048a3209
msgid "Solid Mechanics"
msgstr "固体力学"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:45 0de9acb3afd044dfb3b988e6cb9c0278
msgid ""
"Linear elasticity, hyperelasticity, contact, and plasticity — a progressive "
"solver ladder."
msgstr "线弹性、超弹性、接触与塑性——一条循序渐进的求解器进阶之路。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:47 90a4b8c27cdb4dae8141565f4a62df41
msgid "Fluid Mechanics"
msgstr "流体力学"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:52 8bf0eb168bff4fa8871941ed9f0e2143
msgid ""
"Incompressible Navier-Stokes: cavity, cylinder flow, Rayleigh-Bénard, and "
"more."
msgstr "不可压缩 Navier-Stokes：方腔流、圆柱绕流、Rayleigh-Bénard 对流等。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:54 c812952ff37c49758a50b359017efad9
msgid "Magnetostatics"
msgstr "静磁学"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:59 9fc3de7f2d0b4ca1a777221b2b3f568c
msgid ""
"3D Maxwell: magnetic field around a wire via a stabilized nodal curl-curl "
"formulation."
msgstr "三维 Maxwell：通过稳定化的节点旋度-旋度（curl-curl）格式求解导线周围的磁场。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:61 e11f62b6c2184afdbfdb59deaf6d56bf
msgid "Inverse Design & Identification"
msgstr "反向设计与参数辨识"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:66 47296accc2d245dd850b73a79ed10cbe
msgid ""
"Differentiable FEM: coefficient-field identification and density-based "
"topology optimization."
msgstr "可微有限元方法：系数场辨识与基于密度的拓扑优化。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:68 a581f3ec0cb340ecb07453ce86456760
msgid "Physics-Informed Learning"
msgstr "物理信息学习"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:73 c14fa1ed4e554ecca2951b1a76eb69ea
msgid ""
"Train a neural network to minimize the assembled Galerkin residual ``||K u -"
" F||²``."
msgstr "训练神经网络以最小化装配得到的 Galerkin 残差 ``||K u - F||²``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:75 36765ffef2804afcbfaa82229dd81603
msgid "ML Datasets"
msgstr "机器学习数据集"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:80 6356ecc06a1e4682a9c6c00fc414340c
msgid ""
"Batch generation of heat and wave snapshots for training neural operators."
msgstr "批量生成热方程与波动方程的快照，用于训练神经算子。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:82 6166c75093ef4d66a25cdbd9ac82a241
msgid "Distributed FEM"
msgstr "分布式有限元方法"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/index.rst:87 73883e4942fd44f2b60fa52b51da5dfd
msgid ""
"Graph coloring, spectral partitioning, and multi-GPU assembly benchmarks."
msgstr "图着色、谱划分，以及多 GPU 装配性能基准测试。"

